sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CreateCmd as /create-test-repo
    participant GH as GitHub CLI
    participant Scaffold as File Scaffolder
    participant Repo as Test Repository
    
    User->>CreateCmd: /create-test-repo nhs-digital
    CreateCmd->>GH: gh repo list --limit 200
    GH-->>CreateCmd: Existing repos list
    CreateCmd->>CreateCmd: Auto-detect next version (v22)
    CreateCmd->>GH: gh repo create tractorjuice/arckit-test-project-v22-nhs-digital
    GH-->>Repo: Create public repo
    CreateCmd->>Scaffold: Generate files
    Scaffold->>Repo: .claude/settings.json
    Scaffold->>Repo: .devcontainer/devcontainer.json
    Scaffold->>Repo: README.md, CLAUDE.md
    Scaffold->>Repo: projects/000-global/.gitkeep
    Scaffold->>Repo: docs/README.md
    CreateCmd->>Repo: git commit + push
    CreateCmd-->>User: Summary report
